Rating: 3
I spread this mix on a large piece of Kabul bread, then cut it into bite size pieces before broiling. My guests loved the crunchy/sweet combination. Mix holds up if you prepare it one day in advance.

Rating: 3
I made it using the 3 inch pitas and after splitting them I cut them in half before broiling. Think that the half moon shape was easier to handle than a wedge. My guests loved them and asked for the recipe.

